# Pagination Standards

## Backend Pagination

- Use Laravel's built-in pagination
- Return pagination metadata in consistent format
- Support search and filtering with pagination

Reference: `app/Http/Controllers/TodoController.php`

## Frontend Pagination Component

- Create reusable pagination components
- Support page jumping and previous/next navigation
- Display current page information
- Preserve state and scroll position

## Search and Filter Integration

- Combine pagination with search and filters
- Preserve filter state during pagination
- Reset to page 1 when filters change

## Performance Considerations

- Use appropriate page sizes (10-25 items per page)
- Implement cursor-based pagination for large datasets when needed
- Consider infinite scroll for mobile interfaces
- Cache pagination results when appropriate
